	person("Mark", "Newman", email = "mark@trinetteandmark.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX dissertation templates from
    Harrisburg University, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while preserving a flexable analysis style. Based on Ben
	Marwick's huskydown.
Maintainer: Mark Newman <mark@trinetteandmark.com>
